
Pebble Watchface I put together.
- Vibrates when you connect/disconnect from Bluetooth.
- Indicates when in 'Silent' mode.
- Features:
  - Step/Total Counts
  - Date, Time
  - Temperature, Weather Conditions
  - Battery Level Percentage
  - Connection State

To Get Started:
- Clone this repo.
- Install Pebble SDK: https://developer.pebble.com/sdk/download/

To Build:
pebble build

To Deploy:
pebble install --phone x.x.x.x

Notes:
- Weather hardcoded to pull from this URL (in src/pkjs/index.js): http://forecast.weather.gov/MapClick.php?lat=42.358429&lon=-71.059769&FcstType=json
